move Partners for violations."}},s5Title:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"5. Attribution"}},s5Text:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"Attribution occurs when a new user registers a card with a valid promo code. Self-referral is prohibited. One commission per card. Invalid or inactive codes do not attribute."}},s6Title:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"6. Commission"}},s6Text:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"Commission accrues only on confirmed card activation payment (after template discount). The default rate is set in the Operator's system configuration and is currently 30%; this value is configurable. The Operator may change the rate for the Program as a whole or for an individual Partner; the current rate is shown in the Partner cabinet and applies to new activations. Amounts are in KZT, rounded to whole numbers."}},s7Title:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"7. Partner cabinet"}},s7Text:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"The cabinet shows clicks, cards, activations, earned, available, and paid amounts. Statistics are informational; internal Operator records prevail in disputes. Partners are responsible for account security."}},s8Title:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"8. Payouts"}},s8Text:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"Payout may be requested when available balance reaches 10,000 (ten thousand) KZT or higher minimum set by the Operator. Full available balance is paid in one request; partial payouts are not supported. One active request at a time. Paid via Kaspi or Halyk to profile details. Processing typically within 14 business days."}},s9Title:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"9. Prohibited conduct"}},s9Text:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"Prohibited: self-referral; fraud; spam and misleading ads; harming Shaqyrtu reputation; unlawful promotion or content violating common moral principles; impersonating official representatives without permission. Violations may void commissions and terminate participation."}},s10Title:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"10. Taxes"}},s10Text:{t:0,b:{t:2,i:[{t:3}],s:"Partners are solely responsible for taxes on earnings un